    "description": "宇佐见堇子可不是什么普普通通的高中生，她如此异于常人以至于幻想乡都将她视为异类。堇子可以在她的梦里造访这片幻想之地。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248430/extras/5313ef9755fb02e6d1a5a095d92094a1.avif?t=1752154065\" width=608 height=160 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >异变又又又发生啦！幻想乡陷入了睡眠者造成的克隆人战争。</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248430/extras/d8ce56b57195a9e3d9b5743dc84e90fc.poster.avif?t=1752154065\" width=448 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248430/extras/d8ce56b57195a9e3d9b5743dc84e90fc.webm?t=1752154065\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248430/extras/d8ce56b57195a9e3d9b5743dc84e90fc.mp4?t=1752154065\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Artificial Dream in Arcadia（ADiA）是一款第一人称地牢闯关DRPG，玩家将会扮演宇佐见堇子，穿梭复杂的迷宫，收服各式各样的东方角色，并与她们一起投入回合制战斗。对堇子来说，她拥有幻想乡中唯一可以操控这些异变克隆人的道具——她崭新的手机，由她来解决这异变再合适不过了。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你喜欢的东方角色一抓一大把</h2>异变克隆人正在幻想乡的土地上肆意妄为！她们被称为睡眠者，样貌与现存的东方角色别无二致。堇子可以通过她的手机应用来和睡眠者进行弹幕对决，若获胜则可收服她们。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248430/extras/0d0c53f14d0b2256e3709c67a8f3810b.poster.avif?t=1752154065\" width=448 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248430/extras/0d0c53f14d0b2256e3709c67a8f3810b.webm?t=1752154065\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248430/extras/0d0c53f14d0b2256e3709c67a8f3810b.mp4?t=1752154065\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>若你在弹幕对决中取胜，你可以将睡眠者添加到队伍中，或将她们转化为有用的道具！游戏中你还可以将复数睡眠者合成为一个崭新的存在。<br>将睡眠者添加至队伍会加大你的电池耗电量，若电量耗尽，你将会失去操纵睡眠者和地图的能力，请在探险时做好充分的准备。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248430/extras/6d49ac6a1e76ea1e4e1daff9632b9661.avif?t=1752154065\" width=608 height=160 /></span><br><br>本游戏附赠一套电脑桌面壁纸，请在游戏文件此位置查看 \\Touhou Artificial Dream in Arcadia\\wallpapers",
